 "name": "RPlog_Runther_Interviews_Piper",
 "title": "Runther Interviews Piper",
 "summary": "Over coffee, the concerned Piper checks on the shaken Alexis, who recounts being threatened by a man in the lobby who mistook her for a woman named 'Shanna' working for someone called 'Rogers,' demanding she tell her Twi'lek boss to lay off and warning about money. Rattled and afraid for her safety, Alexis wonders aloud whether the stranger is tied to recent terrorism, while Piper, noting how many odd and dangerous things have been happening lately, urges her to take on security guards regardless of whether she makes any accusations. With Runther and Tavek also present, the scene weaves mistaken identity, intimidation, and the creeping menace surrounding the group.",
